{"tid":1426440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟反擊戰 - 要贏就一定要針對政府痛處","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:10:53.000Z","uid":242182,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6913c656b725a06aaa830f39fac5e54e5b83a06","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"由六月開始可以睇得出，香港政府對遊行、勇武留守、自殺、不合作運動、單日大罷工都無動於衷，因為針唔銡到肉唔知痛。我唔係唔反對以上方式，而係想講我地要搵一個合法方式令政府切身處地出現針銡到肉。<br />\n<br />\n由6月到而家，政府唯一一次唔係好似錄音機咁回應，就係二百萬人遊行之後暫緩。但其實當時仲有一件事，就係連登仔開始向各國要求取消建制派外國國藉。先勿論佢地係咪單單因為咁而暫緩，但係前日林鄭記招、琴日中聯辦記招睇得出，佢地最緊張係經濟，特別係中國而家處於貿易戰中。我地要做嘅，係點樣乘貿易戰作出經濟反擊。而佢地對於機場癱瘓隻字不提，正正表示我地必需針對機場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">設立罷工眾籌，癱瘓機場</span></span><br />\n我知道大家一直有提及癱瘓機場，但好多時都係提議霸路阻止人入機場，只係政府只會覺得可以用武力驅散所以無動於衷。今次提議如下：<br />\n首先搵多位社會知名人士作為信託人去眾籌至少5千萬(即約5萬人每人捐1,000)，確保所籌得金錢唔會比人貪污走。然後罷工只罷一個行業：機場員工，5千萬（當然最後可能不止5千萬)罷工基金會用係所有參與罷工嘅機場員工薪金上損失。而罷工並唔係單日，而係政府一日唔回應，一日繼續罷工癱瘓機場，當眾籌去到目標後就擇日正式開始。"},{"pid":"ecc1988aa7058ceeb376212b36e3f86876533261","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5855671c8b569447656d8d2e9cd255a5d8450af6","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"614cf6314c7826d8ff182a6ced2c237838c24bf8","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"726234ac1282baebf955ddf5b3b30acc8af41993","tid":1426440,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"而家係抗爭關鍵時期!大家真係要傾!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1426270/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1426270/page/1</a><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0f8212a0b0c0ed6794f731276d092bfe78feae","tid":1426440,"uid":249026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"支持眾籌"},{"pid":"6330531068f32accf5f3653cc1b6f8591a43a9a4","tid":1426440,"uid":205180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:04.000Z","msg":"金融，航空，兩大命脈。"},{"pid":"0bec96207a8878dc92db807414e136c73a0af347","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"多謝大家有反應，既然政府唔care勇武，我地就要比佢地知我地有幾大people power"},{"pid":"558124253c9ada58804d1670f1647c4569aaf674","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"有無可能搵到當日做眾籌嘅手足入黎？"},{"pid":"53fb71bf8ab9ab2e03ccc2ecc9ec22c1cf10d62a","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6327be8f3ffa3a61853b816b05173637f5e4a64","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:41:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3aabdbe1a3d655fd61ff8d9580a226b94ef3f451","tid":1426440,"uid":158727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a83b3a15198d6df4e9607ffabd4d92174aa6c1","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6ba914a3510e42d8b4dcf42b3a64d0e8ae62af40","tid":1426440,"uid":22063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭記者會有樣嘢由頭到尾都係冇提過<br />\n就係機場罷工以致200班機取消<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1425525/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1425525/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f1993207922a3c732878ae03260dc930539f3d3e","tid":1426440,"uid":242182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"